---
---

<section
   class="relative mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-10 px-4 pt-24 pb-16 text-center sm:px-6 sm:pt-32 sm:pb-24"
   aria-label="Apresentação"
>
   <a
      href="#rubi"
      class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border/60 bg-card/60 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground backdrop-blur transition-colors hover:border-primary/40 hover:text-foreground"
   >
      <span
         class="inline-flex size-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary shadow-[0_0_12px_oklch(0.7729_0.1535_163.2231)]"
      ></span>
      Rubi 2.0 · agente que opera o seu ERP
      <svg
         class="size-3 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5"
         viewBox="0 0 24 24"
         fill="none"
         stroke="currentColor"
         stroke-width="2"
         ><path
            d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
      >
   </a>

   <h1
      class="max-w-5xl text-5xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] text-foreground text-balance sm:text-7xl md:text-[5.5rem] md:leading-[0.95]"
   >
      Operações que
      <span class="relative inline-block">
         <span
            class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary via-primary/80 to-primary/40 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >se gerenciam</span
         >
      </span>
      sozinhas.
   </h1>

   <p
      class="max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground text-pretty sm:text-xl"
   >
      Montte é o ERP brasileiro construído ao redor de uma agente de IA.
      Financeiro, contatos, serviços e cobranças — tudo conversando entre si,
      tudo conversando com você.
   </p>

   <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 sm:flex-row">
      <a
         class="group inline-flex h-12 items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-foreground px-6 text-sm font-semibold text-background shadow-lg shadow-primary/10 transition-all hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/30"
         href="/dashboard"
      >
         Começar grátis
         <svg
            class="size-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg
         >
      </a>
      <a
         class="inline-flex h-12 items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border/60 bg-card/60 px-6 text-sm font-semibold text-foreground backdrop-blur transition-colors hover:border-border hover:bg-card"
         href="#produto"
      >
         Ver demonstração
      </a>
   </div>

   <div
      class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground"
   >
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
         <svg class="size-3.5 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
            ><path
               d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"
               stroke="currentColor"
               stroke-width="2.5"
               stroke-linecap="round"
               stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
         >
         Sem cartão
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
         <svg class="size-3.5 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
            ><path
               d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"
               stroke="currentColor"
               stroke-width="2.5"
               stroke-linecap="round"
               stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
         >
         Pague pelo uso
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
         <svg class="size-3.5 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
            ><path
               d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"
               stroke="currentColor"
               stroke-width="2.5"
               stroke-linecap="round"
               stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
         >
         Hospedado no Brasil
      </span>
   </div>
</section>
